tldr: The user requested a review of the sleep questionnaire implementation
  against acceptance criteria. The agent then implemented key missing features,
  including a tiredness severity scale with safety warnings, detection for
  COMISA, and logic for Insufficient Sleep Syndrome, updating both the web and
